lead_paragraph: Formula One's new tire contract with Pirelli from 2017 has yet to be signed off with the sport's governing body, despite being agreed in October, as the Italian firm wants specific targets and testing guarantees written in.

headline.print_headline: Testing Agreement Delaying Pirelli F1 Tire Contract
